#: ../../source/user_guide/time_integration.rst:185
#: dc082f6686a346848517bb3b399065c6
msgid ""
"The full driver assembles ``M`` and ``K`` once, builds the time-stepped "
"operator once, condenses it once, then loops:"
msgstr "完整的驱动器只装配一次 ``M`` 和 ``K``\\ ，只构建一次经时间步进处理后的算子，只对其凝聚一次，然后进入循环："

#: ../../source/user_guide/time_integration.rst:221
#: 8ba0ebb07f9746baa20d45f8735ef9cb
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"The two ingredients that make this loop fast are (a) factorising the time-"
"stepped operator only once — the per-step solve is a back-substitution "
"through ``A_in`` — and (b) reusing the cached condenser layout via "
":meth:`~tensormesh.Condenser.condense_rhs`. Together they turn what looks "
"like an order-:math:`N^{3}` problem into an order-:math:`N` inner loop."
msgstr ""
"使这个循环变快的两个要素是：（a）只对经时间步进处理后的算子分解一次 —— 每步的求解只是通过 ``A_in`` 进行一次回代 —— 以及（b）通过 "
":meth:`~tensormesh.Condenser.condense_rhs` 复用缓存的凝聚器布局。两者结合，将一个看似 "
":math:`N^{3}` 阶的问题变成了一个 :math:`N` 阶的内层循环。"

