#: ../../source/user_guide/time_integration.rst:273
#: c30e046061754234b4f79cbbbb78bd94
msgid ""
"The class verifies that ``a`` is lower-triangular and that :math:`\\sum_i "
"b_i = 1` (to within floating-point tolerance), so you catch transcription "
"mistakes early. The same pattern with "
":class:`~tensormesh.ode.ImplicitLinearRungeKutta` gives you diagonally-"
"implicit or fully-implicit schemes — supply a non-zero diagonal and the "
"class will assemble and solve the block stage system for you."
msgstr ""
"该类会验证 ``a`` 是下三角的，并且 :math:`\\sum_i b_i = 1`\\ （在浮点容差范围内），从而让你尽早发现誊写错误。对 "
":class:`~tensormesh.ode.ImplicitLinearRungeKutta` 采用同样的模式，可以得到对角隐式或全隐式格式 —— "
"提供一个非零对角线，该类便会为你装配并求解分块的级系统。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/time_integration.rst:284
#: 2773dbad071d4e0d9094cfd1f580a61e
