msgstr "与边界条件组合"

#: ../../source/user_guide/time_integration.rst:286
#: 88d9de51cbdc4bec97f6b516da345e1a
msgid ""
"Static condensation via :class:`~tensormesh.Condenser` (see "
":doc:`boundary_conditions`) is the recommended way to enforce Dirichlet "
"conditions in TensorMesh. Both time-integration styles support it; the only "
"difference is *where* the three condenser calls go."
msgstr ""
"在 TensorMesh 中，通过 :class:`~tensormesh.Condenser` 进行静态凝聚（参见 "
":doc:`boundary_conditions`\\ ）是施加狄利克雷条件的推荐方式。两种时间积分风格都支持它；唯一的区别在于这三个凝聚器调用 "
"*放在哪里*\\ 。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/time_integration.rst:292
#: 0821bcf22396439caab3a4d84058621a
msgid "Mental model — what each solve is *for*"
msgstr "心智模型 —— 每次求解究竟 *为了什么*"

#: ../../source/user_guide/time_integration.rst:295
#: 7c6b94acda8b4414b07426c7a18b1db4
msgid ""
"The two styles differ in **what the linear solve is solving for**, and that "
"single fact dictates which ``Condenser`` calls are correct:"
msgstr "这两种风格的区别在于 **线性求解到底在求解什么**\\ ，而这一点就决定了哪些 ``Condenser`` 调用才是正确的："

#: ../../source/user_guide/time_integration.rst:298
#: 7109f8699c984b43af80b57c8bba05ca
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"**Manual loop** → the unknown is the **state** :math:`u^{n+1}`. It takes the"
" prescribed value :math:`u_o` on the boundary, so you use the BC-value-aware"
" calls (``condense_rhs`` subtracts :math:`K_{io}\\,u_o`; ``recover`` writes "
":math:`u_o` back into the boundary slots)."
msgstr ""
"**手动循环** → 未知量是 **状态** :math:`u^{n+1}`\\ 。它在边界上取规定值 :math:`u_o`\\ "
"，因此你使用感知边界值的调用（\\ ``condense_rhs`` 会减去 :math:`K_{io}\\,u_o`\\ ；\\ "
"``recover`` 会将 :math:`u_o` 写回边界位置）。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/time_integration.rst:303
#: 2dda52b63f004ba7a1a3c7c32aa04c22
msgid ""
"**Integrator hooks** → the unknown is a **stage slope** :math:`k_i \\approx "
"\\dot u`. A Dirichlet DOF is fixed in time, so :math:`\\dot u = 0` there "
"*whatever* :math:`u_o` is — the slope is zero on the boundary. You use the "
"BC-value-free projections (``restrict`` / ``prolong``, which apply zero on "
"the boundary in both directions)."
msgstr ""
"**积分器钩子** → 未知量是 **级斜率** :math:`k_i \\approx \\dot u`\\ "
"。狄利克雷自由度在时间上是固定的，因此无论 :math:`u_o` 是多少，那里都有 :math:`\\dot u = 0` —— "
"斜率在边界上为零。你使用与边界值无关的投影（\\ ``restrict`` / ``prolong``\\ ，它们在两个方向上都在边界处取零）。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/time_integration.rst:310
#: 6d2a5b3a368240b195138d6e33941661
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"The full-DOF state's boundary value is carried along by :math:`u_0` through "
"the RK update :math:`u_{n+1} = u_0 + h\\sum_i b_i k_i`; it is *not* re-"
"imposed by the stage recovery."
msgstr ""
"全自由度状态的边界值由 :math:`u_0` 通过 RK 更新 :math:`u_{n+1} = u_0 + h\\sum_i b_i k_i` "
"一路携带；它 *不会* 被级恢复重新施加。"

