msgstr "在循环之前调用 ``condenser(A, _)`` *一次*\\ ，以在内部自由度上对经时间步进处理后的算子进行分解；"

#: ../../source/user_guide/time_integration.rst:342
#: c7f32b32fd044fe3a73a5ab1036470b2
msgid ""
"call ``condenser.condense_rhs(f)`` *every step* to project the new RHS down "
"to the interior;"
msgstr "*每一步* 调用 ``condenser.condense_rhs(f)``\\ ，将新的右端项投影到内部；"

#: ../../source/user_guide/time_integration.rst:344
#: 14c06bd4b84d4d3ca830c9df6b2184f9
msgid ""
"call ``condenser.recover(u_in)`` after every solve to glue boundary values "
"back in."
msgstr "在每次求解后调用 ``condenser.recover(u_in)``\\ ，把边界值重新拼接回去。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/time_integration.rst:347
#: a08cf010ddde476d8cfbf2f1b6f26ab0
msgid ""
"For time-varying boundary data, swap in the new values between steps with "
":meth:`~tensormesh.Condenser.update_dirichlet` — the sparsity layout is "
"cached and survives the update, so this call is cheap."
msgstr ""
"对于随时间变化的边界数据，可在步与步之间用 :meth:`~tensormesh.Condenser.update_dirichlet` 换入新值 ——"
" 稀疏布局是缓存的，并能在更新后保留下来，因此这个调用很廉价。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/time_integration.rst:352
#: 055f09569d3c405697b4235e5155e199
msgid "Through the integrator classes"
msgstr "通过积分器类"

#: ../../source/user_guide/time_integration.rst:354
#: c2c3ac87754a4b95be6a20695f14c4d9
msgid ""
":class:`~tensormesh.ode.ImplicitLinearRungeKutta` (and its concrete "
"subclasses) exposes three hooks that the ``step()`` method calls in the "
"right places for static condensation to work end-to-end. Each hook is a no-"
"op by default — override only the ones you need."
msgstr ""
":class:`~tensormesh.ode.ImplicitLinearRungeKutta`\\ （及其具体子类）公开了三个钩子，\\ "
"``step()`` 方法会在恰当的位置调用它们，以使静态凝聚端到端地工作。每个钩子默认都是空操作 —— 只重写你需要的那些即可。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/time_integration.rst:363
#: b9315cdd0123479ca53a61f9ed33688b
msgid "Hook"
msgstr "钩子"

#: ../../source/user_guide/time_integration.rst:364
#: 40af7d0619dc4e5eb1f7ef6e3aa92fb7
