msgid "once per ``[i][j]`` block of the stage system"
msgstr "级系统的每个 ``[i][j]`` 块一次"

#: ../../source/user_guide/time_integration.rst:368
#: df2f120a2c524345a6019d70bc4648c0
msgid "the condensed inner block, ``condenser(K)[0]``"
msgstr "凝聚后的内部块，\\ ``condenser(K)[0]``"

#: ../../source/user_guide/time_integration.rst:369
#: 9701edce931e4c6a90b95f307e623151
msgid "``pre_solve_rhs(f)``"
msgstr "``pre_solve_rhs(f)``"

#: ../../source/user_guide/time_integration.rst:370
#: abb9f59588fd465d815024c4393ba447
msgid "once per stage RHS"
msgstr "每个级的右端项一次"

#: ../../source/user_guide/time_integration.rst:371
#: a8b5ef81c7b544b5934ef351e3a8c16b
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"the *restriction* to inner DOFs, ``condenser.restrict(f)`` — **not** "
"``condense_rhs(f)``: a stage slope is zero on the boundary by construction, "
"so the :math:`-K_{io}\\,u_o` correction term in ``condense_rhs`` would over-"
"apply the BC."
msgstr ""
"向内部自由度的 *限制*\\ ，\\ ``condenser.restrict(f)`` —— **而非** ``condense_rhs(f)``\\"
" ：级斜率在构造上即在边界处为零，因此 ``condense_rhs`` 中的 :math:`-K_{io}\\,u_o` 修正项会过度施加边界条件。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/time_integration.rst:376
#: 72e6d6bf0a29471f84964eb94510b8e6
msgid "``recover_stage(k_i)``"
msgstr "``recover_stage(k_i)``"

#: ../../source/user_guide/time_integration.rst:377
#: f9afbdf3bc67486fbb2737de84afb341
msgid "once per stage, after the solve"
msgstr "每个级一次，在求解之后"

#: ../../source/user_guide/time_integration.rst:378
#: c235c75382d044498fe18256464829aa
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"the prolongation to full DOF with zero in the boundary slots, "
"``condenser.prolong(k_i)`` — **not** ``recover``, which would write the "
"Dirichlet value into the boundary slots and break the increment ``u_{n+1} = "
"u_n + h\\sum_i b_i k_i``."
msgstr ""
"向全自由度的延拓，且边界位置取零，\\ ``condenser.prolong(k_i)`` —— **而非** ``recover``\\ "
"，因为后者会把狄利克雷值写入边界位置，破坏增量 ``u_{n+1} = u_n + h\\sum_i b_i k_i``\\ 。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/time_integration.rst:383
#: a0fefaac15d64aff964d1ee094160945
msgid ""
"The fourth hook, ``post_solve(u)``, runs after the stage slopes have already"
" been lifted and combined with :math:`u_0`, so ``u`` is always full-DOF when"
" it sees you. Use it for things that act on the final state (clamping, "
"normalisation, projection onto a manifold) rather than for boundary "
"recovery."
msgstr ""
"第四个钩子 ``post_solve(u)`` 在级斜率已经被提升并与 :math:`u_0` 组合之后运行，因此当它接触到 ``u`` 时，\\ "
"``u`` 始终是全自由度的。请将它用于作用在最终状态上的操作（裁剪、归一化、投影到流形上），而不是用于边界恢复。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/time_integration.rst:389
#: aae3f00b97c84b9d95eefac6056c3d5c
msgid ""
"The same three hooks cover multi-stage schemes unchanged: ``step()`` calls "
"them once per stage (``pre_solve_lhs`` once per ``[i][j]`` block), so a "
":class:`~tensormesh.ode.MidPointLinearEuler` or a custom "
":class:`~tensormesh.ode.ImplicitLinearRungeKutta` tableau wires up exactly "
"like the backward-Euler example below."
msgstr ""
"这同样的三个钩子无需改动即可覆盖多级格式：\\ ``step()`` 每个级调用它们一次（\\ ``pre_solve_lhs`` 每个 "
"``[i][j]`` 块一次），因此一个 :class:`~tensormesh.ode.MidPointLinearEuler` 或自定义的 "
":class:`~tensormesh.ode.ImplicitLinearRungeKutta` 表，其接线方式与下面的后向欧拉示例完全相同。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/time_integration.rst:395
#: ba787db2002b41769e07bb1650171e45
msgid "Putting them together, a heat-equation driver becomes:"
msgstr "把它们组合起来，一个热方程驱动器就变成了："

