#: 14152aa51fb74b85b0dd04e5515eb158
msgid ""
"The ``examples/diffusion/heat/`` directory ships both versions: ``heat.py`` "
"(manual loop) and ``heat_ode.py`` (integrator class). They produce identical"
" snapshots to machine precision — try them side by side."
msgstr ""
"``examples/diffusion/heat/`` 目录提供了两个版本：\\ ``heat.py``\\ （手动循环）和 "
"``heat_ode.py``\\ （积分器类）。它们生成的快照在机器精度内完全相同 —— 不妨并排试一试。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/time_integration.rst:438
#: 744eb180511547da9d28f66f06262ba4
msgid "Why ``restrict`` / ``prolong`` and not ``condense_rhs`` / ``recover``"
msgstr "为什么用 ``restrict`` / ``prolong`` 而非 ``condense_rhs`` / ``recover``"

#: ../../source/user_guide/time_integration.rst:440
#: c08be8f721044ab08640c8d5a7d3cfb4
msgid ""
"The two integrator hooks operate on the **stage slope** :math:`k_i \\approx "
"\\dot u`, not on the state :math:`u` itself. At a Dirichlet DOF :math:`u` is"
" held fixed in time, so :math:`\\dot u = 0` there *regardless* of the "
"prescribed value. The two BC-value-aware methods on "
":class:`~tensormesh.Condenser` are designed for the state:"
msgstr ""
"这两个积分器钩子作用于 **级斜率** :math:`k_i \\approx \\dot u`\\ ，而非状态 :math:`u` "
"本身。在狄利克雷自由度处，\\ :math:`u` 在时间上保持固定，因此 *无论* 规定值为何，那里都有 :math:`\\dot u = 0`\\ "
"。\\ :class:`~tensormesh.Condenser` 上那两个感知边界值的方法是为状态而设计的："

#: ../../source/user_guide/time_integration.rst:447
#: a13c60501d8e47d7bac5d6f7ba70ad22
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
":meth:`~tensormesh.Condenser.condense_rhs` subtracts :math:`K_{io}\\,u_o` "
"from the inner RHS to account for the state's prescribed boundary values;"
msgstr ""
":meth:`~tensormesh.Condenser.condense_rhs` 从内部右端项中减去 :math:`K_{io}\\,u_o`\\ "
"，以计入状态所规定的边界值；"

#: ../../source/user_guide/time_integration.rst:450
#: f6c4b38d0bf9462f97855befe0338d44
msgid ""
":meth:`~tensormesh.Condenser.recover` writes :math:`u_o` into the boundary "
"slots of the lifted solution."
msgstr ":meth:`~tensormesh.Condenser.recover` 将 :math:`u_o` 写入提升后解的边界位置。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/time_integration.rst:453
#: d0b695a9a36145d9bb33713ae317bab2
msgid ""
"Use those when condensing the state-space system (the manual loop). For "
"stage slopes inside the integrator, use the BC-value-free projections "
":meth:`~tensormesh.Condenser.restrict` and "
":meth:`~tensormesh.Condenser.prolong`, which apply zero on the boundary in "
"both directions. The difference vanishes for homogeneous Dirichlet (where "
":math:`u_o = 0`), but matters as soon as the prescribed values are non-zero."
msgstr ""
"在凝聚状态空间系统（即手动循环）时使用它们。而对于积分器内部的级斜率，则使用与边界值无关的投影 "
":meth:`~tensormesh.Condenser.restrict` 和 "
":meth:`~tensormesh.Condenser.prolong`\\ ，它们在两个方向上都在边界处取零。对于齐次狄利克雷（此时 "
":math:`u_o = 0`\\ ），二者的差别会消失；但一旦规定值非零，差别就立刻显现出来。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/time_integration.rst:461
#: 2fe853ab4c734552b6813c9d14540cea
msgid "The bug is invisible under homogeneous Dirichlet"
msgstr "在齐次狄利克雷条件下这个 bug 不可见"

#: ../../source/user_guide/time_integration.rst:464
#: f5849e6ec5b143cbbc00ac7db671e9f4
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Mixing up the two pairs costs nothing when :math:`u_o = 0`, which is exactly"
" why it slips through. Make it non-zero and it shows immediately. Take the "
"heat problem above but hold the whole boundary at :math:`u_o = 1` (interior "
"starting at zero), backward Euler, :math:`\\Delta t = 10^{-2}`, 40 steps, "
"and measure against the manual state-space loop (``condense_rhs`` / "
"``recover``) as the reference:"
msgstr ""
"当 :math:`u_o = 0` "
"时，混用这两对方法毫无代价，而这恰恰是它能蒙混过关的原因。把它改成非零，问题就会立刻显现。取上面的热传导问题，但将整个边界固定在 :math:`u_o "
"= 1`\\ （内部从零开始），采用后向欧拉法，\\ :math:`\\Delta t = 10^{-2}`\\ ，40 步，并以手动状态空间循环（\\"
" ``condense_rhs`` / ``recover``\\ ）作为参考进行测量："

